Book 1, Book 2, Book 3...

11
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:37,812
This takes forever.

12
00:00:37,812 --> 00:00:41,899
Quantum Computer: Checks ALL 1 million books at the SAME TIME.

13
00:00:41,899 --> 00:00:43,593
Finds your book instantly.

14
